-   Added libcurl error 52 handling consensus [\[PR#403\]](https://github.com/skalenetwork/skaled/pull/403)

**SKALE Admin ()**

-   Fixed dry run disabling [\[PR#327\]](https://github.com/skalenetwork/skale-admin/pull/327)
